title: 111: The Target Haul Episode: July '20 Edition!
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode: July '20 Edition!
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are taste-testing finds from Target: mini stuffed pancakes, sous-vide eggs, buffalo cauliflower wings, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, 2 different sausages that are SO GOOD! The gang also tries a super-tasty Starbucks drink that only has 45 calories. So go ahead, push play now, and when you’re done, you can find a list of the products mentioned in the episode on our Foodcast page!
itunes:summary: We’re heading to Target in this week’s edition of Chew the Right Thing!
